    {
      "end": 96.87999725341797,
      "text": "When I'm falling down",
      "start": 94.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 100.9800033569336,
      "text": "How could I forget, the city where we lost it all",
      "start": 96.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 104.36000061035156,
      "text": "Knew it would recover",
      "start": 102.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 108.5999984741211,
      "text": "Cause we're only human, yeah, we're only human now",
      "start": 104.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 110.72000122070312,
      "text": "And we found each other",
      "start": 108.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 114.5999984741211,
      "text": "Hidden under the ruins, so nothing could ruin us",
      "start": 110.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 131.74000549316406,
      "text": "Hidden in the ruins, the ruins of happiness",
      "start": 128.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 134.9199981689453,
      "text": "Walk around and you'll see what happens when you use negativity",
      "start": 131.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 137.77999877929688,
      "text": "To cause pain, sorrow and anxiety",
      "start": 135.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 139.67999267578125,
      "text": "We are human, only human",
      "start": 137.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 142.24000549316406,
      "text": "Excuses, cop outs, you're scapegoats",
      "start": 139.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 144.9199981689453,
      "text": "But you can't escape folks, this is the bed you made",
      "start": 142.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 146.9199981689453,
      "text": "So lie down, rest your head",
      "start": 145.02000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 148.97999572753906,
      "text": "On all the unnecessary dead",
      "start": 146.9199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 150.3800048828125,
      "text": "And those you fill with dread",
      "start": 148.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 152.8000030517578,
      "text": "It's not too late, turn around",
      "start": 150.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 155.0800018310547,
      "text": "Mend the wounds, plant the seeds in the ground",
      "start": 152.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 157.74000549316406,
      "text": "But if you turn your back, then that's that",
      "start": 155.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 159.74000549316406,
      "text": "There won't be coming back",
      "start": 158.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 161.4199981689453,
      "text": "So choose, make a choice",
      "start": 159.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 164.13999938964844,
      "text": "Think of all of those without a voice",
      "start": 161.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 168.13999938964844,
      "text": "So forced to sit here with the hurting",
      "start": 164.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 172.6199951171875,
      "text": "And all the things that takes them away",
      "start": 168.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 176.89999389648438,
      "text": "You can't hear or at least you don't listen",
      "start": 172.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 178.13999938964844,
      "text": "Yeah",
      "start": 177.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 181.33999633789062,
      "text": "You're my safety net",
      "start": 179.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 183.3800048828125,
      "text": "You catch me when I fall",
      "start": 181.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 185.13999938964844,
      "text": "When I'm falling down",
      "start": 183.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 190.13999938964844,
      "text": "How could I forget, the city where we lost it all",
      "start": 185.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 193.22000122070312,
      "text": "Knew it would recover",
      "start": 191.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 195.5800018310547,
      "text": "Cause we're only human",
      "start": 193.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 197.63999938964844,
      "text": "Yeah, we're only human now",
      "start": 195.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 199.22000122070312,
      "text": "And we found each other",
      "start": 197.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 201.8000030517578,
      "text": "Hidden under the ruins",
      "start": 199.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 204.22000122070312,
      "text": "So nothing could ruin us",
      "start": 201.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 210.22000122070312,
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh",
      "start": 205.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 211.3800048828125,
      "text": "Yeah",
      "start": 210.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 216.05999755859375,
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh",
      "start": 211.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 221.39999389648438,
      "text": "Now I'm lost for what we used to be",
      "start": 218.0399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 225.5,
      "text": "And I'm still sitting here with this new degree of life",
      "start": 221.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 228.39999389648438,
      "text": "When you told me you would be here still",
      "start": 225.5
    },
    {
      "end": 233.3000030517578,
      "text": "Who cut the cord, who cut the net from me",
      "start": 229.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 236.4600067138672,
      "text": "I still wanted you on my team",
      "start": 233.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 240.1199951171875,
      "text": "To the darkness I thought the light would bring us here",
      "start": 236.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 245.22000122070312,
      "text": "But we're still incomplete with fear in our heart",
      "start": 240.1199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 248.83999633789062,
      "text": "There is a bright light above",
      "start": 245.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 253.32000732421875,
      "text": "And here's a place where we can start and be more like ourselves",
      "start": 248.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 257.3399963378906,
      "text": "And here, not let that fear lead the way",
      "start": 253.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 261.4200134277344,
      "text": "I'm asking you to find a way past your own thing",
      "start": 257.5199890136719
    },
    {
      "end": 264.1600036621094,
      "text": "That thinks it's selfishness that keeps us here",
      "start": 261.4200134277344
    },
    {
      "end": 267.82000732421875,
      "text": "It's just us, we're human my dear",
      "start": 264.1600036621094
    },
    {
      "end": 270.3999938964844,
      "text": "You're my safety net",
      "start": 268.5
    },
    {
      "end": 272.4599914550781,
      "text": "You catch me when I fall",
      "start": 270.3999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 274.4599914550781,
      "text": "When I'm falling down",
      "start": 272.70001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 276.5400085449219,
      "text": "How could I forget",
      "start": 274.4599914550781
    },
    {
      "end": 279.4599914550781,
      "text": "The city where we lost it all",
      "start": 276.5400085449219
    },
    {
      "end": 282.2799987792969,
      "text": "Knowing we'll recover",
      "start": 280.239990234375
    },
    {
      "end": 286.7799987792969,
      "text": "Cause we're only human, yeah, we're only human now",
      "start": 282.4599914550781
    },
    {
      "end": 288.70001220703125,
      "text": "And we found each other",
      "start": 286.7799987792969
    },
    {
      "end": 290.82000732421875,
      "text": "Hidden under the ruins",
      "start": 288.70001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 293.4599914550781,
      "text": "So nothing could ruin us",
      "start": 290.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 299.6000061035156,
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh",
      "start": 294.79998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 300.4200134277344,
      "text": "Yeah",
      "start": 299.6000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 304.4200134277344,
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh",
      "start": 300.4200134277344
    }
